BRIEF: Toggle brief room description mode

Syntax: brief
        brief on
        brief off
        brief status

DESCRIPTION:
  In brief mode you receive shorter room descriptions when you move.
  The room name and exits are still displayed; the full description
  is omitted.

  Your brief setting is saved between logins.

COMMANDS:
  brief
      Toggles between brief and verbose mode.

  brief on
      Enables brief mode.

  brief off
      Disables brief mode (returns to verbose).

  brief status
      Shows whether brief mode is currently on or off.

SEE ALSO: look, score
